  "detailed_description": "Espionage Activity is an isometric stealth action game where you sneak into a heavily guarded corporate office. <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Ascend a diorama-like office tower with over 40 floors. <br></li><li>Solve increasingly complex stealth encounters. <br></li><li>Evade guards with straightforward but robust mechanics. <br></li><li>Collect log files to uncover the secrets of the XYZ Corporation. </li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sneak</h2> Pass undetected through encounters with the building’s security force. Use your dashing technique to creatively manoeuvre through patrol routes. With no gadgets or weapons, understanding your enemy is the key to success.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2842200/extras/393816cf4e2ee5d47433ee67e45765b2.poster.avif?t=1722356338\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2842200/extras/393816cf4e2ee5d47433ee67e45765b2.webm?t=1722356338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2842200/extras/393816cf4e2ee5d47433ee67e45765b2.mp4?t=1722356338\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Attack</h2> Use close-quarters combat to incapacitate anyone who gets too close. Turn unsuspecting guards into projectiles with the throw technique, and use them to open new paths forward.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2842200/extras/3b267e99bf2dbdc9085385cc02f1e994.poster.avif?t=1722356338\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2842200/extras/3b267e99bf2dbdc9085385cc02f1e994.webm?t=1722356338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2842200/extras/3b267e99bf2dbdc9085385cc02f1e994.mp4?t=1722356338\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Escape</h2> Detection means near-certain capture. Make split-second decisions to reach the next floor before the area enters lockdown.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2842200/extras/44d0a03966506c5950bf36912bfe1619.poster.avif?t=1722356338\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2842200/extras/44d0a03966506c5950bf36912bfe1619.webm?t=1722356338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2842200/extras/44d0a03966506c5950bf36912bfe1619.mp4?t=1722356338\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
